Netflix has published its list of recommended TVs for 2019, detailing which TVs you should be using to enjoy the best experience possible on the streaming platform. The company publishes its list every year, based on certain criteria which ensure that the models listed deliver an impressive Netflix experience. For TVs to achieve a recommendation from Netflix, they must fulfil at least five of seven criteria listed by the streaming platform. These criteria are based around the responsiveness of the app, the quality of the video, and the accessibility of the Netflix menu. Below are the specific criteria for Netflixâ€™s recommended TVs, of which five are required to be included in the list: Only selected TV models carry the Netflix Recommended logo in 2019, but Netflix said that additional brands would be added as they become available and are designated. Below are the current TV models recommended by Netflix.   